User->>API: Upload Resume + Job Description

API->>Workflow: Start optimization workflow

Workflow->>Parser: Parse resume

Parser-->>Workflow: Canonical Resume Model

Workflow->>Retriever: Retrieve relevant experience

Retriever-->>Workflow: Ranked context

Workflow->>Planner: Generate optimization plan

Planner-->>Workflow: Structured plan

Workflow->>Rewriter: Rewrite selected sections

Rewriter->>LLM: Structured rewrite request

LLM-->>Rewriter: JSON response

Rewriter->>Guardrails: Validate AI output

Guardrails-->>Rewriter: Safe structured output

Rewriter->>Validator: Business validation

Validator-->>Workflow: Approved changes

Workflow->>ATS: Calculate ATS score

ATS-->>Workflow: ATS report + recommendations

Workflow->>Renderer: Generate LaTeX

Renderer-->>Workflow: Compiled PDF

Workflow->>Storage: Store .tex, PDF, and metadata

Workflow-->>API: Optimization completed

API-->>User: PDF + ATS Report + Change Summary